 (starting wealth)/10 per level"}, "522b0e2d-ab4e-410c-994a-5889c341a484": {"name": "Stubbornness", "tags": ["Disadvantage", "Mental"]}}}}, "notes": {"a3fd9589-ac68-479c-acf7-68c83009b1b9": {"text": "Features: Taboo Traits (Jumping, Running skills)\n\nFor their Intolerance disadvantage, the primary racial enemies of the dwarves are orcs and dragons. Many also dislike elves; this can be part of their Intolerance (with no point change) or a separate quirk. Similarly, some dwarves (particularly among Thulin\u2019s Folk) truly hate Megalans.\n\nMany dwarves lack Greed or Miserliness, a great many are Honest, and some have Phobia (Open Spaces). Night Vision is very common. Some have extra points in Signature Gear; each point is worth an additional $500 in equipment."}}}